comment_data.body:
And here, perhaps

``` haskell
fromObject o = V.fromList <$> fromObject o
-- or point-free
fromObject = fmap V.fromList . fromObject
```

The disadvantage is that the error message will be about "list" instead of "Vector", but I think that's not very important.
